sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Test as SPFreshTest
    participant Idx as SPANN::Index
    participant Extra as ExtraDynamicSearcher
    participant Router as PostingRouter
    participant PD as TiKV PD
    participant Pool as splitThreadPool
    participant Worker as Worker Node
    participant TiKV as TiKV Store

    Note over Test,TiKV: === Insert 一个 Vector 的完整流程 ===
    
    Test->>Idx: AddIndex(vectorSet)
    Idx->>Extra: AddIndex(vector, VID)
    
    Extra->>Extra: RNGSelection() → 选出 head replicas<br/>[headID_1, headID_2, ...]
    
    Note over Extra,TiKV: --- 对每个 replica headID ---
    
    rect rgb(255, 243, 205)
        Note over Extra,Router: ★ PostingRouter 介入点
        Extra->>Router: GetOwner(headID)
        Router->>PD: GetKeyLocation(headID)
        PD-->>Router: KeyLocation{regionId, leaderStoreAddr}
        Router->>Router: 匹配 leaderStoreAddr<br/>→ NodeStores 数组
        
        alt isLocal = true (leader 在本 Node 绑定的 Store)
            Router-->>Extra: RouteTarget{isLocal=true}
            Extra->>Extra: AsyncAppend(headID, posting)
            Extra->>TiKV: db->Get(headID) 读当前 posting
            TiKV-->>Extra: currentPosting
            Extra->>Extra: 拼接 newPosting = current + append
            Extra->>TiKV: db->Put(headID, newPosting)
        else isLocal = false (leader 在其他 Node 的 Store)
            Router-->>Extra: RouteTarget{nodeIndex=1}
            Extra->>Router: SendRemoteAppend(nodeIndex=1, headID, posting)
            Router->>Worker: Socket RPC: RemoteAppendRequest
            Worker->>Worker: appendCallback → Append()
            Worker->>TiKV: db->Get + db->Put
            Worker-->>Router: RemoteAppendResponse{Success}
            Router-->>Extra: ErrorCode::Success
        end
    end
    
    Note over Extra,TiKV: === Append 后的级联操作 ===
    
    alt postingSize > postingSizeLimit + bufferSizeLimit
        Extra->>Extra: 同步 Split()
    else postingSize > postingSizeLimit
        Extra->>Pool: SplitAsync(headID)
        
        Note over Pool,TiKV: --- Split 执行 ---
        Pool->>TiKV: db->Get(headID) 读 posting
        Pool->>Pool: KMeans 聚类 → 2 个新 posting
        Pool->>Extra: HeadIndex.AddIndex(newHead1, newHead2)
        Pool->>TiKV: db->Put(newHead1, posting1)
        Pool->>TiKV: db->Put(newHead2, posting2)
        Pool->>TiKV: db->Delete(oldHeadID)
        Pool->>Extra: HeadIndex.DeleteIndex(oldHeadID)
        
        Note over Pool,TiKV: --- Split 后 Reassign ---
        loop 每个散落向量 v
            Pool->>Pool: CheckIsNeedReassign(v)
            alt v 离新 head 太远
                Pool->>Pool: ReassignAsync(v, headPrev)
                Pool->>Pool: RNGSelection(v) → 找更近的 head
                Pool->>Extra: Append(newHeadID, v)<br/>⚠️ 本地执行，不经过 Router
                Extra->>TiKV: db->Get + db->Put
            end
        end
    end
    
    alt postingSize < mergeThreshold
        Extra->>Pool: MergeAsync(headID)
        
        Note over Pool,TiKV: --- Merge 执行 ---
        Pool->>Extra: SearchHeadIndex() → 找邻近 head
        Pool->>TiKV: db->Get(neighborHead) 读邻近 posting
        Pool->>Pool: 合并两个 posting
        Pool->>TiKV: db->Put(survivor, mergedPosting)
        Pool->>TiKV: db->Delete(victim)
        Pool->>Extra: HeadIndex.DeleteIndex(victim)
        
        Note over Pool,TiKV: --- Merge 后 Reassign ---
        loop 被合并 posting 中每个向量 v
            alt v 离存活 head 比被删 head 远
                Pool->>Pool: ReassignAsync(v, survivorHead)
                Pool->>Pool: RNGSelection(v) → 找新 head
                Pool->>Extra: Append(newHead, v)<br/>⚠️ 本地执行
            end
        end
    end
    
    Note over Test,TiKV: === SaveIndex / Checkpoint ===
    Test->>Idx: SaveIndex()
    Idx->>Extra: Checkpoint()
    loop 每 20ms
        Extra->>Pool: AllFinished()?
        Pool-->>Extra: jobsize / currentJobs
    end
    Note over Extra: 等待所有 Split/Merge/Reassign 完成
    Extra->>TiKV: 保存 VersionMap
